# 002 — Materials, dispersion models & units spine (Part D)

## Spec reference

- `C:\GitHub\Berreman\specs\0022\.spec-md` — parent spec (Spec 0022). This slice owns **Part D**.
- `C:\GitHub\Berreman\specs\0022\.slices\001.slice-md` — slice 001 (Part A), which created the five projects, the test project, and the units-spine architecture this slice fills in.
